lead_paragraph: Sebastian Vettel's expletive-laden radio rants betray his frustration at Ferrari's fading form, according to his former Red Bull team mate Daniel Ricciardo and predecessor Fernando Alonso.

headline.print_headline: Vettel Rage Due to Ferrari Frustration, Say Rivals
